    &lt;p&gt;To add integrated text or buttons before and&#x2F;or after any text-based &lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;input&amp;gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;..&#x2F;components&#x2F;#input-groups&quot;&gt;check out the input group component&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
